**Location**: `/Users/robert/Code/MittwaldCoWork/mittwald-mcp/evals/scripts/scenario-runner.ts` and `/Users/robert/Code/MittwaldCoWork/mittwald-mcp/evals/scripts/agent-e2e-runner.ts`

