**Location**: `/Users/robert/Code/MittwaldCoWork/mittwald-mcp/src/utils/tool-scanner.ts` and `/Users/robert/Code/MittwaldCoWork/mittwald-mcp/src/constants/tools.ts`

Tools are discovered and registered dynamically:

